<p id="kicker">Smartcard</p>


<div id="outline-container-1" class="outline-1">
<h1 id="sec-1">The OpenPGP card</h1>
<div class="outline-text-1" id="text-1">

<p>The OpenPGP Card is a specification of an ISO 7816-4,-8 compatible
smartcard and also an actually available implementation of this
specification as a standard sized card.
</p>


<a href="graphics/newcard-f.jpg"><img
src="graphics/newcard-f-small.jpg" alt="Front matter"
width="200" height="127" class="lfloat"/></a>
<p>
Front (click to enlarge)
</p>


<p style="clear: both"/>
<a href="graphics/newcard-fs.jpg"><img
src="graphics/newcard-fs-small.jpg" alt="Front matter (ID-000)"
width="200" height="127" class="lfloat"/></a>
<p>
ID-000 version
</p>


<p style="clear: both"/>
<a href="graphics/newcard-b.jpg"><img
src="graphics/newcard-b-small.jpg" alt="Back matter"
